OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FClear skies
OL,6,Fto start but some low cloud in the
OL,7,Fwest and north later, with fog patches
OL,8,Fforming overnight mainly in the south.
OL,9,FRemaining dry and relatively mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FEarly fog clearing, then
OL,12,Fdry and very mild with warm sunny
OL,13,Fspells during Wednesday. Winds slowly
OL,14,Fease throughout the day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,17,FBreezy with rain or showers Thursday.
OL,18,FLikely wet and windy at first Friday,
OL,19,Fthen cooler with showers. Saturday
OL,20,Fstarts off settled before rain arrives
OL,21,Fduring the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
